window.bookSummaryJSON = "Narnia...where the woods are thick and cool, where the Talking Beasts are called to life, a new world where the adventure begins. <p>Digory and Polly meet and become friends one cold, wet summer in London. Their lives burst into adventure when Digory's Uncle Andrew, who thinks he is a magician, sends them hurtling to...somewhere else. They find their way to Narnia, newborn from the Lion's song, and encounter the evil sorceress Jadis, before they finally return home.</p> <p>This was the sixth book written in <i>The Chronicles of Narnia</i>. It now stands as the first book in the series.</p>"; 
